{"tid":1754584,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【泛民請入】一齊加速抗爭進度 引爆憲政危機","createTime":"2019-11-25T09:10:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T11:52:25.000Z","uid":173207,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"6768cdb52b11f44afa3b4f27f268cbcb19484e0b","tid":1754584,"uid":173207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:10:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好沉迷區選勝利<br />\n要救poly足之餘 仲有好多野可以做 要抗爭真普選蒞臨為止</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/dog2_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/dog2_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/dog2_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">一齊share 逼政府回應 再等美國介入</span><br />\n重點就係：<br />\n<blockquote>不過，我們的目標是取消功能組別達至普選，而不是小修小補完善它。因此，新任區議員如何利用這個機會動搖劉國勳的地位，將可成為民主抗爭的重炮台。</blockquote><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\nSource: <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2rqCmnW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2rqCmnW&d=S%2FsiG%2FBE2bBILTWTz3VeJiWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=7fae1d5a\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2rqCmnW</a><br />\n<br />\n劉國勳敗選，他是否喪失了區議會（第一）功能界別資格？<br />\n<br />\n先不講條例，任何一個有羞恥的人在面對這種情況，都應該在程序啟動前自動請辭。一個醫學界議員如果被醫委會釘牌，他就失去了代表醫學界的資格，賴死唔走就是自取其辱。<br />\n<br />\n《立法會條例》39（4）條：「任何人如在提名期結束後已不再與某功能界別有密切聯繫，則該人即喪失當選為該功能界別的議員的資格。」<br />\n<br />\n不過，多虧「袋住先」方案，2012年的修訂把區議會第一和第二剔出第39條所限，但很明顯在修訂的過程中，並沒有周詳考慮到區議會界別的立法會議員落選區會的情況。<br />\n<br />\n在周浩鼎落選的情況，他應當仍具備超區的議員資格，理由是他在區議會選舉的基礎上，還有350萬港人的選民機礎，剝奪他的資格等同剝奪了264,399選民選擇周浩鼎的民意授權。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>然而，區議會第一界別是由452位區選員間選產生，區議會換屆，劉國勳的選民基礎已不復再，換言之立法會內已無議員代表452位區議員的權益和聲音，在外國，這形同觸發一個憲政危機，需要憲法法院裁決修補漏洞。劉國勳為免香港憲制受到挑戰，理應自動辭職替政府解圍。</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不過，我們的目標是取消功能組別達至普選，而不是小修小補完善它。因此，新任區議員如何利用這個機會動搖劉國勳的地位，將可成為民主抗爭的重炮台。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n作者"},{"pid":"ecfb9e94f171a7417d99eae4c735f193777373f0","tid":1754584,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:11:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">依家我哋區選贏咗，外國好關注我哋！<br />\n係咪連少少嘢都唔肯做呀？</span><br />\n<br />\n最新的tweets 一定響bot <br />\n總之<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"> Retweet Like Reply </span></span>就得<br />\n㩒入👉 <a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=S%2FsiG%2FBE2bBILTWTz3VeJiWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=d4fc604e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打 <span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">/task</span></span> 攞任務<br />\n<br />\nSen. Marco Rubio<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenRubioPress/status/1198773889112956928\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRubioPress%2Fstatus%2F1198773889112956928&d=S%2FsiG%2FBE2bBILTWTz3VeJiWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=709a9b0e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRubioPress%2Fstatus%2F1198773889112956928&h=2dc87735\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SenRubioPress/status/1198773889112956928</a><br />\n<br />\nSen. Rick Scott<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenRickScott/status/1198739997911846913\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRickScott%2Fstatus%2F1198739997911846913&d=S%2FsiG%2FBE2bBILTWTz3VeJiWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=34c15edb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRickScott%2Fstatus%2F1198739997911846913&h=291b9b3e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SenRickScott/status/1198739997911846913</a><br />\n<br />\nSen. Marsha Blackburn<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/MarshaBlackburn/status/1198773803976810496\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMarshaBlackburn%2Fstatus%2F1198773803976810496&d=S%2FsiG%2FBE2bBILTWTz3VeJiWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=56b98ff2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMarshaBlackburn%2Fstatus%2F1198773803976810496&h=03c18e02\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/MarshaBlackburn/status/1198773803976810496</a><br />\n<br />\n更加多嘅tweet請入bot搵<br />\n<br />\n（twitter戰線)國際都關注今次香港的區選<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1754022\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1754022</a>"},{"pid":"9cf3732fde2a6f6b57b2dccf6ea0c117497b98a2","tid":1754584,"uid":173207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:14:33.000Z","msg":"1/10 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"278404e9de91a52c506218406e3496379fa39058","tid":1754584,"uid":173207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:14:45.000Z","msg":"2/10 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce77b8d2fd06cdce300a51f7d5c5706480bc7112","tid":1754584,"uid":173207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:15:16.000Z","msg":"3/10 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8618cafe390d30b802ac2dcf4be900a368cd83a6","tid":1754584,"uid":65449,"like":0,"disli